   GET /api/v1/generation/models - Lista dostÄ™pnych modeli
   POST /api/v1/generation/text-to-image
   POST /api/v1/generation/edit-image
   GET /api/v1/generation/history
   DELETE /api/v1/generation/{id}

2. ASYSTENT AI (Chatbot)
   POST /api/v1/chat/messages - Send message
   GET /api/v1/chat/conversations/{id} - Get conversation
   DELETE /api/v1/chat/conversations/{id}
   POST /api/v1/chat/conversations/{id}/export

3. ASYSTENT GÅOSOWY (Voice)
   POST /api/v1/voice/transcribe - Speech to Text
   POST /api/v1/voice/synthesize - Text to Speech
   GET /api/v1/voice/languages

4. KREATYWNY ASYSTENT (Content)
   POST /api/v1/content/generate - Generate content
   GET /api/v1/content/templates - List templates
   POST /api/v1/content/publish - Publish to social media
   GET /api/v1/content/calendar - Content calendar

5. BIZNES BOT (Orchestration)
   POST /api/v1/bizbot/query - Send query
   GET /api/v1/bizbot/capabilities - List available actions
   POST /api/v1/bizbot/execute-action - Execute tool

6. ANALITYK DANYCH (Data Analysis)
   POST /api/v1/analytics/upload - Upload CSV
   POST /api/v1/analytics/query - Ask question
   GET /api/v1/analytics/report/{id}

7. AUTOMATYZATOR (Automation)
   GET /api/v1/automation/templates - List templates
   POST /api/v1/automation/create - Create automation
   GET /api/v1/automation/{id}/status
   DELETE /api/v1/automation/{id}

8. AUTH & USERS
   POST /api/v1/auth/register
   POST /api/v1/auth/login
   POST /api/v1/auth/refresh
   GET /api/v1/auth/me
   POST /api/v1/auth/logout

DATABASE SCHEMA:

```sql
-- Users
CREATE TABLE users (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  email VARCHAR UNIQUE,
  password_hash VARCHAR,
  name VARCHAR,
  plan VARCHAR (starter/business/enterprise),
  created_at TIMESTAMP,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Conversations (Chat)
CREATE TABLE conversations (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES users,
  title VARCHAR,
  messages JSONB,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Generations (Images)
CREATE TABLE generations (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES users,
  prompt TEXT,
  model VARCHAR,
  image_url VARCHAR,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Content (Blog Posts, Social)
CREATE TABLE content (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES users,
  type VARCHAR,
  title VARCHAR,
  content TEXT,
  status VARCHAR (draft/published),
  published_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Automations
CREATE TABLE automations (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES users,
  template_id VARCHAR,
  config JSONB,
  status VARCHAR (active/inactive),
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Usage Tracking
CREATE TABLE usage_logs (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES users,
  feature VARCHAR,
  tokens_used INT,
  cost DECIMAL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);
```

INTEGRACJE ZEWNÄ˜TRZNE:

1. Image Generation:
   - Replicate API (Flux models)
   - OpenAI API (DALL-E 3)
   - Stability AI API (Stable Diffusion)

2. LLMs:
   - Google Gemini 2.0 API (main chatbot)
