   - Google Cloud Speech-to-Text
   - ElevenLabs API (TTS)

4. Content Publishing:
   - WordPress XML-RPC
   - Medium API
   - LinkedIn API
   - Instagram Graph API

5. Analytics:
   - Google Analytics API
   - Shopify GraphQL API
   - Stripe API

6. Automation:
   - n8n Webhooks
   - Zapier API

AUTHENTICATION & SECURITY:
- JWT tokens (access + refresh)
- Rate limiting (Cloudflare rate limiting)
- CORS properly configured
- Input validation on all endpoints
- SQL injection prevention
- HTTPS only
- CSRF protection

CACHING STRATEGY:
- Redis dla frequently accessed data
- Cloudflare Cache dla static assets
- Browser cache headers (max-age)

StwÃ³rz peÅ‚ny kod backendu jako gotowy projekt w Express.js lub Hono.
