## CZÄ˜ÅšÄ† VIII: NARZÄ˜DZIA I TECHNOLOGIE (2025)

### Frontend Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 + React 19
- **UI**: shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS
- **State**: Zustand / Jotai
- **Data Fetching**: TanStack Query v5
- **Animation**: Framer Motion
- **Charts**: Recharts / ECharts
- **Real-time**: Socket.io / WebSockets
- **TypeScript**: v5.6

### Backend Stack
- **Runtime**: Node.js 22 LTS
- **Framework**: Hono / Express.js
- **Database**: Supabase (PostgreSQL)
- **Cache**: Cloudflare KV / Redis
- **ORM**: Prisma / Drizzle ORM
- **Auth**: NextAuth.js / Auth0
- **Validation**: Zod
- **Logging**: Pino / Winston

### AI Integrations
- **Image**: Replicate / DALL-E 3 / Flux.1
- **LLM**: Google Gemini 2.0 / OpenAI GPT-4.5
- **Voice**: Google Cloud Speech / ElevenLabs
- **Data**: DuckDB WASM / LangChain

### DevOps
- **Hosting**: Cloudflare Workers / Vercel
- **Database**: Supabase
- **Monitoring**: Sentry / LogRocket
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions
- **Version Control**: GitHub

